ormed about how we collect, use, and disclose personal information. If we change the Privacy Statement in a material way, we will provide appropriate notice to you.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<h3>CONTACTING US<\\/h3>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>If you have any questions, comments, or concerns about this privacy policy, email us at&nbsp;<a href=\\\"mailto:contact@Solar-America.org\\\">contact@Solar-America.org<\\/a>.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>This policy was last updated December 9th, 2016.<\\/p>\",\"_token\":\"Aot2s0NFNOIVdFbQUt6geCZmFygqJFp8yjUysiJZ\",\"_previous_\":\"http:\\/\\/solar-program.test:800\\/admin\\/footer-menu\"}', '2019-03-23 14:22:24', '2019-03-23 14:22:24'),
